title: Video: Thomas makes 232-yard ace in Rd. 3 of WGC
text:
RSS 
Justin Thomas is having a decent season. 
The 23-year-old has wins at the CIMB Classic , SBS Tournament of Champions and shot 59 during his victory at the Sony Open. He also added a hole-in-one to his résumé on Saturday at the WGC-Mexico Championship . 
And not just any hole-in-one, but a slam dunk on the 232-yard par-3 13th hole:
